replies.body:
it is called utility, more focus on setting up allies for success, than on own play.  Teamwork is OP.

"Support" weak solo power, but empowers their 4 allies
if you have 3 Supports = 
Support "X"  (-1)+1+1 = 2{{champion:16}} 
Support "Y"  (-1)+1+1 = 2{{champion:555}} 
Support "Z"  (-1)+1+1 = 2{{champion:37}} 
Normal Champ "A" (1)+1+1+1 = 4{{champion:102}} 
Normal Champ "B" (1)+1+1 +1= 4{{champion:51}} 
Team total power = 2+2+2+4+4 = 14

(Parentheses = what a champs solo power is)

Compare to team with only 1 support
Support "Z" (-1) = -1{{champion:267}} 
Normal Champ "A" (1)+1 = 2{{champion:81}} 
Normal Champ "B" (1)+1= 2{{champion:11}} 
Normal Champ "C" (1)+1 = 2{{champion:875}} 
Normal Champ "D" (1)+1 =2{{champion:134}} 
Team Power = -1+2+2+2+2 = 7

Please note this is an example, not true to ~life~ scale.
